"{\"uid\": \"nypost.com-2024-08-06-real-estate-olympic-gold-medalist-shaun-white-sells-la-home-for-3-92m\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Snowboarding legend Shaun White has cashed in on his Hollywood Hills home, selling it for $3.92 million.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaun White\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\"}, {\"begin\": 53, \"end\": 68, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Hills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.578742424198838e-27, \"text\": \"Hollywood Hills\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Hills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Hills\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three-time Olympic gold medalist snagged the midcentury-modern Los Angeles house for $3.75 million in 2018, the same year he won his last gold medal in Pyeongchang.\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999982951522, \"rank\": 1.3410845673652062e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"score\": 0.9739820807490616, \"rank\": 0.026712934216414616, \"text\": \"Pyeongchang\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite listing the property for $5 million in April, retired Louis Vuitton executive Michael Silvaggi sealed the deal for less, reports theWall Street Journal.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.190614664858342e-21, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 1950s home, spanning 1,900 square feet on a third of an acre, is located in the coveted Outpost Estates, known for its celebrity residents.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Made up of three bedrooms and two baths, it features a kidney-shaped pool, a fire pit and panoramic city views from floor-to-ceiling windows.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You can see people walking up the trail from a distance,\\\" Chase Rogers of Beverly Hills Estates, who represented the buyer, told the Journal.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Real_Housewives_of_Beverly_Hills\", \"score\": 0.9998674838287657, \"rank\": 0.0001325336263373631, \"text\": \"Beverly Hills\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Real_Housewives_of_Beverly_Hills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Real_Housewives_of_Beverly_Hills\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Silvaggi plans to renovate the property with his partner, Steven Bouwman, who runs the design firm Studio Veren.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Bouwman\", \"score\": 0.9999999994108748, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bouwman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Bouwman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Bouwman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The home's distinctive midcentury architecture and spectacular views were major draws.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rogers noted the appeal of midcentury-modern homes in LA, emphasizing the property's spacious yard.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you think of LA, you think of cool architecture, land and views,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The house was previously available for rent for $17,000 per month.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"White, now 37, has shifted his primary residence to a redbrick ranch in southern Nevada.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nevada\", \"score\": 0.9999999996837232, \"rank\": 3.159439748041347e-10, \"text\": \"Nevada\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nevada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nevada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been seen attending the Paris Olympics this summer and is the first snowboarder to win gold at three separate Winter Games.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, White launched his own snowboard brand, Whitespace.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.9955970275518021, \"rank\": 0.004064077313844454, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whitespace_character\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.872315885287374e-19, \"text\": \"Whitespace\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whitespace_character\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whitespace_character\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listing representatives Rick Tyberg and Lauren Duffy of Douglas Elliman declined to comment on the transaction.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"score\": 0.9188010814887198, \"rank\": 0.08819873400399104, \"text\": \"Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\"}, {\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Elliman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Douglas Elliman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Elliman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Elliman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, homes in Outpost Estates had a median sale price of $2.9 million, according to Redfin.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Outpost_Estates,_Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999212022741, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Outpost Estates\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Outpost_Estates,_Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Outpost_Estates,_Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": []}]}"